{"tid":1173084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士：住8樓以上跳樓自殺多","createTime":"2019-05-27T00:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T02:59:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"603a9bcbd980dd16d36055a83758d89cd8de3d14","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190527/20688393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688393&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=b100f349\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688393&h=7005ca2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190527/20688393</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞士：住8樓以上跳樓自殺多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190527/large/13480758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F13480758.jpg&h=7b5ae90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾繁光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上文提及的2013年瑞士伯恩大學研究顯示，居住高層比住低層的人更易跳樓自殺，居住地下及一樓跳樓自殺的男性，佔總自殺個案的19%、女性為23%；而住八樓以上跳樓的男性，佔自殺個案27%，女性佔31%。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：加國：居25樓以上病發零存活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：都市化令人更易患病<br />\n<br />\n精神專科醫生曾繁光指出，香港並沒有相關研究足以證明居住樓層與精神健康有關，「有英國研究顯示喺上世紀七、八十年代，住喺高樓大廈更易有情緒問題，但因為佢哋本身喺健康上需要政府照顧，先被調上高樓，所以無法咁簡單就推論高樓同情緒病有關，反而係都市化就令更多人患上情緒病」。<br />\n<br />\n曾解釋，樓宇高度以外，不同的社會、經濟狀況對精神健康有更大影響，「生活壓力大，社會過份講求競爭力，逼都市人不斷生產，工作過程刻板亦會令人情緒唔好」。他解釋，都市人患上精神或情緒病，絕非單一原因，由生活、工作、食物，乃至小時候所接受的教養方式，都會影響精神健康。<br />\n<br />\n對於住在高樓大廈容易令人產生跳樓的傾向，曾繁光認為，自殺的方法並非取決於居住樓層，反而是不同地方人們所能接觸的自殺方法，「住平房嘅人會選擇跳橋，農村會選吞食農藥，美國吞槍等，唔代表住高樓，自殺嘅風險會大咗」。<br />\n<br />\n相反，住得較高，景觀開揚一點，又會否令人心曠神怡，減低自殺率？曾繁光表示，對於精神病患者來說，開揚景觀亦可能看成「咁靚嘅景，但我咁冇用，一切都冇意思&hellip;&hellip;住得高都未必可以減少精神問題，有焦慮症者反而會擔憂：我一陣點落返去？」  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n香港樓宇沖天建 住得高，身體好？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n加國：居25樓以上病發零存活<br />\n<br />\n加國：居25樓以上病發零存活<br />\n60樓住戶：最怕停電及火警<br />\n環團：座向更影響空氣質素<br />\n香港樓宇沖天建 住得高，身體好？"},{"pid":"526825edd5d9fe8371e8ea1f1ba2b3fdd1039d70","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"住3樓以下跳樓受傷多"},{"pid":"7dfe46ddd0f03879b52d3230a3da4162c690f400","tid":1173084,"uid":54181,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:00:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a156c9d8951ce0be43514448b2b9dc731885369a","tid":1173084,"uid":5523,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"526825edd5d9fe8371e8ea1f1ba2b3fdd1039d70","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"住3樓以下跳樓受傷多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"智商之鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ec24db7e5c114d918065f4d400ac772de683e9","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"漁民海上遇險多"},{"pid":"bd690b2c9fe34c5175a3f5a1ae142d6e5e258cc1","tid":1173084,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"全香港也是癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bcd38884d394a41a3d4077231c02a49614741c","tid":1173084,"uid":204306,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"的士狗炒車多"},{"pid":"c9bd82e22a3a9fbcd2000a3568942f58a61de0ed","tid":1173084,"uid":136833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"塞車因爲車多"},{"pid":"51da68a4852666bd5fd09008abaee0b8b1b15ae2","tid":1173084,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"我睇咗啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1e11fdc231c5e6c62d1d38f62964303c8bb45d","tid":1173084,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"駕車司機車禍多"},{"pid":"8b3332c47219ca0940014992688178468f2bcbd9","tid":1173084,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"我只係知如果住得太高<br />\n收工時間番到屋企時如果急屎嘅話會好痛苦，由其見到啲友明明企喺panel前面<br />\n但掛住睇電話，道門開左都唔去撳制close door嗰陣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0af48d51d113a97c7b6d9b4cb73e9beee7d2261","tid":1173084,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"結論： 想自殺嘅人會自殺"},{"pid":"77652a5e0d15f76a5648a3bacaf855f98fd93819","tid":1173084,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相關新聞：加國：居25樓以上病發零存活</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.reactiongifs.com/r/2013/10/tim-and-eric-mind-blown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reactiongifs.com%2Fr%2F2013%2F10%2Ftim-and-eric-mind-blown.gif&h=67a3cb1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6912f5db7468504c9cc296a2f83573c931de7b35","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"近海吃魚， 住林吃熊掌 <br />\n<br />\n魚與熊掌 不可兼得"},{"pid":"f36f34ac3ac7183053ca438bfadae4d06af0bf9b","tid":1173084,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"瑞士應該9成係8層樓以下"},{"pid":"8188e2fcbdb691380e57f257906cc8e8979e3655","tid":1173084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"孟母三遷"},{"pid":"3d6438e01bd8108a3956493b17815770e46efc60","tid":1173084,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8188e2fcb